carriage and stop the show,

00:16.384 --> 00:17.783
take everyone's breath away.

00:17.817 --> 00:20.085
<i>[Randy] ...what their family
and friends will think of it...</i>

00:20.087 --> 00:21.887
- Positive vibes. Let's go.
- Yes.

00:21.889 --> 00:24.857
