future partner will react to it.</i>

00:24.859 --> 00:27.226
I could see her in
something with, like, topless.

00:28.128 --> 00:29.294
But all bets are off
when it comes to

00:29.296 --> 00:31.964
actually shopping for
that dream dress.

00:31.966 --> 00:34.533
