less than perfection.

00:35.735 --> 00:38.037
With expectations this high,

00:38.039 --> 00:41.106
there's bound to be some
shocking moments along the way.

00:41.274 --> 00:42.875
[both] Wow!

00:42.877 --> 00:44.043
[Monique] Mindy, don't hate me,

00:44.045 --> 00:46.078
I don't like any of them.

00:48.381 --> 00:50.582
[Randy] <i>And the
surprises kept coming.</i>

00:51.651 --> 00:54.453
<i>Today, we're going to
take a look back at</i>

00:54.455 --> 00:56.922
