different around here lately.

01:16.210 --> 01:17.943
Kleinfeld's made a few changes

01:17.945 --> 01:20.512
to take care of our brides
in these uncertain times

01:20.514 --> 01:23.949
while I took care of things
at my other home in Florida.

01:23.951 --> 01:25.217
Well, sort of.

01:25.919 --> 01:26.885
Ah!

01:26.887 --> 01:28.153
Don't get your foot caught.

01:28.155 --> 01:30.155
<i>But we'll talk a little
more about that later.</i>

01:30.157 --> 01:31.857
Okay, let's get back to work.

01:31.859 --> 01:33.926
<i>I may have been over
a thousand miles away,</i>

01:33.928 --> 01:36.195
<i>but I was still in
full bridal mode</i>

01:36.197 --> 01:38.997
<i>and had a blast
surprising all my brides.</i>

01:38.999 --> 01:41.333
<i>- Hello, beautiful.
- [gasps] Randy!</i>

01:41.335 --> 01:43.135
- [Mindy] We have Randy here.
- Hello, beautiful.

01:43.137 --> 01:44.903
Oh, my God!

01:44.905 --> 01:46.939
I'm leaving with a Randy
dress. I hope you know that!

01:46.941 --> 01:48.173
<i>Hey, there!</i>

01:48.175 --> 01:51.677
[gasps] Oh, God, I
dropped a dress, too.

01:51.679 --> 01:54.446
<i>[Randy] Oh, my gosh,
she was so surprised.</i>

01:54.448 --> 01:55.981
So, Daniela is
my production assistant.

01:55.983 --> 01:57.015
Daniela, come here.

01:57.017 --> 01:58.450
- Oh, my gosh.
- Come here, join me.

01:58.452 --> 02:00.619
- [chuckles] Hey, gorgeous.
- Hello.

02:00.621 --> 02:01.820
- How are you?
- Good.

02:01.822 --> 02:03.222
So, you were
obviously surprised.

02:03.224 --> 02:04.957
I was.
But you know what?

02:04.959 --> 02:07.292
I was more surprised
by your brutal honesty.

02:07.294 --> 02:08.994
[laughs]

02:08.996 --> 02:11.964
I was brutally honest, but
that's just 'cause I love you.

02:11.966 --> 02:13.165
Aw!

02:13.167 --> 02:15.134
[Amber] So, what do we think?

02:15.136 --> 02:16.902
[Daniela] It feels
really good on.

02:16.904 --> 02:18.637
I'm not feeling this at all.

02:19.239 --> 02:21.773
- [gasps]
- [all] Wow!

02:21.775 --> 02:24.176
- [Daniela] Okay.
- The honesty, okay, we need that.

02:24.178 --> 02:27.446
<i>[Randy] I'm not a huge
fan of the charmeuse</i>

02:27.448 --> 02:29.848
<i>because it's so silky and shiny</i>

02:29.850 --> 02:33.118
that it shows every
little bump and bulge,

02:33.120 --> 02:35.320
and I don't like
anything about it.

02:35.322 --> 02:36.588
[laughs]

02:36.590 --> 02:42.161
I've never seen this brutally
honest side of Randy before.

02:42.163 --> 02:44.963
<i>I would like to think that
it's a sign of endearment,</i>

02:44.965 --> 02:49.201
<i>but I was not expecting
to get a hard no so quickly.</i>

02:49.203 --> 02:50.936
I just think you
could find something

02:50.938 --> 02:53.372
<i>so much more
beautiful than this.</i>

02:53.374 --> 02:55.140
I knew it came
from a place of love.

02:55.142 --> 02:57.009
It just still really shocked me.

02:57.011 --> 02:58.110
[both laughing]

02:58.112 --> 03:00.279
I mean, I think everyone
was a little surprised

03:00.281 --> 03:03.248
at my harshness, like,
"Wow, he's tough," right?

03:03.250 --> 03:07.186
Yeah. But it ended up working
out in a better way for me

03:07.188 --> 03:11.156
because we ended up finding
something that was more suited...

03:11.158 --> 03:12.658
- Your dress.
- My dress.

03:12.660 --> 03:14.226
- It was your dress.
- Yeah.

03:14.228 --> 03:15.961
All right, she's coming out.

03:15.963 --> 03:17.196
Oh, my gosh!

03:31.144 --> 03:32.277
- Oh.
- Wow!

03:32.279 --> 03:33.845
- Oh, my goodness!
- [all] Wow!

03:33.847 --> 03:37.082
[Amber] This is
absolutely stunning.

03:37.084 --> 03:39.551
Okay, now this is what
I've been waiting for!

03:41.254 --> 03:44.289
You look gorgeous!

03:44.291 --> 03:45.457
[sighs]

03:46.359 --> 03:48.093
[Daniela speaking]

03:48.095 --> 03:49.795
[all laughing]

03:49.797 --> 03:51.096
Do you guys like it?

03:51.098 --> 03:53.465
- Hell yeah.
- Oh, I love it. Love it. Love it.

03:53.467 --> 03:54.433
It's a very special moment.

03:54.435 --> 03:56.501
You're surrounded by
people that love you.

03:57.670 --> 03:59.972
The crew seems to love it.

03:59.974 --> 04:01.473
Randy loves it.

04:01.475 --> 04:02.941
<i>I've found the dress.</i>

04:02.943 --> 04:04.409
It feels so good.

04:04.411 --> 04:09.114
[all] Daniela, are you
saying yes to the dress?

04:09.116 --> 04:12.150
- Yes.
- [all cheering]

04:17.290 --> 04:19.124
That was an amazing day.

04:19.126 --> 04:20.792
It really was.

04:20.794 --> 04:22.160
- I-- - What happened
to your voice?

04:22.162 --> 04:24.363
I was just going to, I
was just going to tell you,

04:24.365 --> 04:26.765
I just got back from
my bachelorette party.

04:26.767 --> 04:28.433
<i>It was a little bit
too much fun.</i>

04:28.435 --> 04:30.302
<i>There was a megaphone involved,</i>

04:30.304 --> 04:31.903
<i>a little bit of screaming.</i>

04:31.905 --> 04:35.173
<i>I don't, I don't know what
happened, but here we are.</i>

04:35.175 --> 04:37.743
So I'm going to-- I'll
let you keep doing this

04:37.745 --> 04:38.744
and I'll come back
in a little bit.

04:38.746 --> 04:40.012
Okay, come back
and check with...

04:40.014 --> 04:41.480
- Okay, okay, perfect.
- Check with me.

04:42.282 --> 04:43.615
She really is amazing.

04:47.186 --> 04:49.254
From last minute wishes...

04:49.256 --> 04:52.057
My wedding is two
and a half months away.

04:52.059 --> 04:53.859
Okay.

04:53.861 --> 04:54.893
Yeah.

04:54.895 --> 04:56.328
The contradicting wishes.

04:56.330 --> 04:59.364
I envision for her
to show a little skin.

05:00.667 --> 05:03.201
- I wouldn't... No.
- [laughs]

05:03.203 --> 05:07.172
Our brides have really thrown
our consultants some curve balls.

05:07.174 --> 05:09.875
