that I can't describe.

06:25.718 --> 06:27.352
You're very beautiful, honey,

06:27.354 --> 06:30.455
and don't ever let anybody
tell you anything different, okay?

06:32.425 --> 06:34.459
I feel like a bride.

06:34.461 --> 06:39.898
[all] Shaela, are you
saying yes to the dress?

06:39.900 --> 06:42.334
- Yes!
- [all cheering]

06:46.406 --> 06:49.941
We did it. Yeah.
I found it.

06:49.943 --> 06:51.243
- I found it.
- It's beautiful.

06:51.245 --> 06:53.912
[all cheering]

06:53.914 --> 06:55.313
<i>[Randy] I mean,
we've seen it all.</i>

06:55.315 --> 06:58.817
Amber, Mindy, and I
tackled a double appointment

06:58.819 --> 07:00.652
