not allowed to see it.

07:06.093 --> 07:07.292
- Come on.
- [Alayna] No.

07:07.294 --> 07:09.094
- Just like a peek.
- [Alayna] I'll give you a hint.

07:09.096 --> 07:10.929
- [Chloe] Okay.
- There's white on it.

07:10.931 --> 07:11.663
[Chloe] Oh, thanks.

07:11.665 --> 07:14.166
[Alayna laughs]

07:14.168 --> 07:17.969
But our bride, Chloe, who
is transgender, surprised us

07:17.971 --> 07:21.139
when we learned just how
monumental it was for her

07:21.141 --> 07:23.175
<i>just to be trying on
wedding dresses.</i>

07:23.177 --> 07:26.178
For me, you know, this
is an amazing experience

07:26.180 --> 07:27.312
'cause I was married
once before,

07:27.314 --> 07:31.583
<i>before I transitioned.
And I was in a tuxedo.</i>

07:31.585 --> 07:33.118
<i>[Randy] This is really exciting</i>

07:33.120 --> 07:37.422
'cause it's really her first time
to really, like, truly be herself.

07:37.424 --> 07:39.191
- Yes.
<i>- [Randy] Yeah.</i>

07:39.193 --> 07:41.126
- [all] Yes.
- Yes. Yes. Yes.

07:42.094 --> 07:45.230
- Yes, absolutely.
- So pretty.

07:45.232 --> 07:47.032
[woman] Yes.
Look at that face.

07:47.034 --> 07:49.034
