07:50.269 --> 07:51.536
[Chloe] Yup.

07:51.538 --> 07:52.904
- This is it.
- [Amber] You love it?

07:52.906 --> 07:53.905
Yeah, I love it.

07:53.907 --> 07:55.106
- Yes.
- Don't look...

07:55.108 --> 07:56.842
You know, there was
a time in my life

07:56.844 --> 07:58.376
