08:09.923 --> 08:11.490
you know, feeling amazing

08:11.492 --> 08:14.626
in this gorgeous dress
at Kleinfeld's, like...

08:14.628 --> 08:16.361
[woman]
Making me cry.

08:18.030 --> 08:21.766
Not just, you know, what
I'm wearing to the wedding,

08:21.768 --> 08:24.302
but just who I am as a
person is different this time.

08:24.304 --> 08:28.039
