whole self into this relationship.

08:28.041 --> 08:30.275
[Randy] <i>It's a
beautiful thing to see</i>

08:30.277 --> 08:33.812
when somebody is able to
really express who they are

08:33.814 --> 08:35.213
and come out of their shell

08:35.215 --> 08:36.915
and not have to hide
from the world.

08:36.917 --> 08:39.417
- Are you ready, Randy?
<i>- [Randy] I'm ready.</i>

08:42.188 --> 08:43.388
Chloe...

08:43.390 --> 08:45.624
[Amber and Randy] ...are
you saying yes to the dress?

08:45.626 --> 08:47.993
- Yes.
- [all cheering]

08:49.529 --> 08:51.630
- [Amber] Congratulations.
- Thank you.

08:51.632 --> 08:52.664
Yes!

09:00.640 --> 09:03.174
