were like, "Yeah, this is it"?

10:15.916 --> 10:17.115
<i>[Carly] Instantly.</i>

10:17.149 --> 10:19.250
[Kassandra] <i>Do you
realize how impressive it is?</i>

10:19.252 --> 10:21.186
