stop me ♪</i>

12:10.464 --> 12:14.332
<i>♪ No, no, nothing can
stop me ♪</i>

12:14.334 --> 12:16.201
While searching for the
perfect wedding dress,

12:16.203 --> 12:19.137
a bride should expect
the unexpected.

12:19.139 --> 12:21.973
They might be shocked
to find themselves in love.

12:21.975 --> 12:23.942
Oh, my God!

12:24.076 --> 12:25.677
